94 kcal mol-1) and 0.0009 {\\AA} by increasing the\nplane-wave cuttoff energy to 850 eV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Feb 2021 01:08:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Feb 2022 23:04:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-04"}
