 \\infty$ and $m \\gg n$. This result is algorithmic, and together\nwith the work of Bansal and Meka characterizes how the discrepancy of each\nrandom hypergraph model transitions from $\\Theta(\\sqrt{d})$ to $o(\\sqrt{d})$ as\n$m$ varies from $m=\\Theta(n)$ to $m \\gg n$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Feb 2021 04:50:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Jul 2021 12:21:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 23 Oct 2021 00:58:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-26"}
