m$ 9.5 hrs for the arrival time and 87 $\\pm$ 111 km\ns$^{-1}$ for the arrival speed. There is no tendency for one spacecraft to\nprovide more accurate arrival predictions than the other.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Feb 2021 11:36:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-16"}
