virtually impossible, TRACB or TRACL\nmethods will be needed in any 2D or 3D simulations involving transition region\nphysics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Feb 2021 13:36:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-07"}
